snippet.title: Panchayat Season 4 - Official Trailer | Jitendra Kumar, Neena Gupta, Raghubir Yadav | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Panchayat Season 4 Official Trailer
Starring Jitendra Kumar, Neena Gupta, Raghubir Yadav, Faisal Malik, Chandan Roy, Sanvikaa, Durgesh Kumar, Sunita Rajwar, Ashok Pathak, Pankaj Jha

A TVF Creation
Created by: Deepak Kumar Mishra, Chandan Kumar
Directed by: Akshat Vijaywargiya, Deepak Kumar Mishra
Written by: Chandan Kumar
Executive Producers: Deepak Kumar Mishra, Vijay Koshy, Shreyansh Pandey

Official Release Date June 24, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Amidst the much-awaited village panchayat elections, Pradhan’s and Bhushan’s camps battle tooth and nail to maintain the upper hand. The future of everyone, including Abhishek, hangs in the balance.

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. snippet.title: Man Escapes Air India Crash by One Flight - He Noticed Something Strange!
snippet.description:
Man Escapes Air India Crash by One Flight - He Noticed Something Strange!


A devastating incident involving Air India Flight 171—a Boeing 787-8 Dreamliner—has resulted in numerous fatalities after the aircraft crashed shortly after takeoff from Ahmedabad airport on its way to London. A passenger who had traveled on the same aircraft just two hours earlier, on a Delhi-to-Ahmedabad leg, took to social media to report troubling technical issues. He pointed out that the air conditioning and in-flight entertainment systems were not functioning, sparking serious concerns about the plane’s upkeep and overall safety.

The tragedy has put a renewed spotlight on Air India’s operational practices, with the passenger’s account raising further doubts about the airline's service standards and safety track record. The Boeing 787-8, equipped with Rolls Royce Trent 1000 engines, has previously encountered mechanical challenges—now prompting investigations into potential system failures or deliberate interference. Indian aviation authorities, in coordination with their British counterparts, are actively probing the cause of the crash amid growing global criticism.

This incident has once again ignited global conversations about the dependability of modern aircraft and the critical need for strict maintenance routines. It also revives scrutiny of Air India’s long-standing reputation, frequently ranked among the least reliable carriers worldwide.

en.title: Man Escapes Air India Crash by One Flight - He Noticed Something Strange!
en.description:
Man Escapes Air India Crash by One Flight - He Noticed Something Strange!


A devastating incident involving Air India Flight 171—a Boeing 787-8 Dreamliner—has resulted in numerous fatalities after the aircraft crashed shortly after takeoff from Ahmedabad airport on its way to London. A passenger who had traveled on the same aircraft just two hours earlier, on a Delhi-to-Ahmedabad leg, took to social media to report troubling technical issues. He pointed out that the air conditioning and in-flight entertainment systems were not functioning, sparking serious concerns about the plane’s upkeep and overall safety.

The tragedy has put a renewed spotlight on Air India’s operational practices, with the passenger’s account raising further doubts about the airline's service standards and safety track record. The Boeing 787-8, equipped with Rolls Royce Trent 1000 engines, has previously encountered mechanical challenges—now prompting investigations into potential system failures or deliberate interference. Indian aviation authorities, in coordination with their British counterparts, are actively probing the cause of the crash amid growing global criticism.

This incident has once again ignited global conversations about the dependability of modern aircraft and the critical need for strict maintenance routines. It also revives scrutiny of Air India’s long-standing reputation, frequently ranked among the least reliable carriers worldwide.

snippet.title: डबल ईंजन इतनी आसानी से फेल नहीं होता, फिर क्या हुआ?
snippet.description:
AI 171 के साथ साथ अस्पताल के हॉस्टल से भी भयावह ख़बरें आ रही हैं। बड़ी संख्या में मेडिकल छात्र गंभीर रुप से घायल हुए हैं। इनमें कितनों की जान नहीं बच सकी है, इसकी आधिकारिक घोषणा नहीं हुई है। गृहमंत्री अमित शाह ने कहा है कि इस दुर्घटना के पीछे कोई साज़िश नहीं है। यह एक दुर्घटना है। अमित शाह ने घटना स्थल का दौरा किया है और शोक संतप्त परिवारों के साथ खड़े रहने का भरोसा दिलाया है। सोशल मीडिया में ड्रीमलाइनर विमानों के रख-रखाव को लेकर सवाल उठ रहे हैं। आने वाले दिनों में इस सवालों पर बहस और साफ होगी लेकिन हमने आरंभिक स्तर पर इन सवालों को भी शामिल किया है। यह घटना बहुत दुखदायी है। काश हमें इस पर वीडियो नहीं बनाना पड़ता।

snippet.description:

snippet.title: ENG vs WI | 3rd T20I | Cricket Highlights | West Indies Tour Of England | 10th June 2025
snippet.description:
England secured a dominant 37-run victory over West Indies in the 3rd T20I at Utilita Bowl, Southampton. Batting first, England posted a massive 248/3 in 20 overs, with Ben Duckett leading the charge with an explosive 84 off 46 balls. West Indies fought hard but fell short, managing 211/8 in their chase. With this win, England completed a 3-0 series sweep, asserting their dominance in the shortest format.

snippet.title: Superman | New Trailer
snippet.description:
On July 11, the entire world will look up. Here's the New Trailer for #Superman - Only In Cinemas and IMAX in English, Hindi, Tamil & Telugu. In 3D & IMAX 3D. 

Website: www.warnerbros-india.com
Facebook:   / warnerbrosindia  
Instagram:   / warnerbrosindia  
X: https://x.com/WarnerBrosIndia 

“Superman,” DC Studios’ first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who’s driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (“Twisters,” “Hollywood”) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (“The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel”) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the “X-Men” movies, “Juror #2”) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (“For All Mankind”), Anthony Carrigan (“Barry,” “Gotham”), Nathan Fillion (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “The Suicide Squad”), Isabela Merced (“Alien Romulus”), Skyler Gisondo (“Licorice Pizza,” “Booksmart”), Sara Sampaio (“At Midnight”), María Gabriela de Faría (“The Moodys”), Wendell Pierce (“Selma,” “Tom Clancy’s Jack Ryan”), Alan Tudyk (“Andor”), Pruitt Taylor Vince (“Bird Box”) and Neva Howell (“Greedy People”).

“Superman” is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (“The Last of Us”) and editors William Hoy (“The Batman”) and Craig Alpert (“Deadpool 2,” “Blue Beetle”).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, “Superman,” which will be in Cinemas and IMAX® in India on July 11, 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

#WarnerBrosIndia #SupermanTrailer

snippet.title: Abdul की बात सुनकर क्यों डर गया Jetha? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Full Movie
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

The watchman receives a tip from Jethalal, who instructs him to pay close attention to his house. Later, Sodhi makes the decision to pose as a burglar in order to test the watchman's skills. Tapu is doing karate while sprinting around the home. Daya devises innovative strategies to apprehend any intruders who might attempt to enter her home. Champaklal comforts Gogi, who is terrified of the robbers. Tapu and his companions agree that they must protect their community from these alleged robbers. To defeat these robbers, they devise a circuit training program. The robbers, meantime, enter the community disguised as repairmen.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 160-162
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTXtajBo1G2UEa_wE8BVSU7

snippet.title: मैंने काशीनाथ के आखों मे कातिया का काल देखा है - Bollywood Action Movie - Sunny Deol - Ghatak
snippet.description:
#b4ufilmy #bollywood #hindi #hindimovie #movie #action #thriller #sunnydeol #meenakshiseshadri

फिल्म का नाम: घातक
कलाकार: सनी देओल, मीनाक्षी शेषाद्रि, अमरीश पुरी और डैनी डेन्जोंगपा
निर्देशक: राजकुमार संतोषी 
म्यूजिक : आर. डी. बर्मन

Movie Name : Ghatak
Cast : Sunny Deol, Meenakshi Seshadri, Amrish Puri, and Danny Denzongpa
Director: Rajkumar Santoshi
Music: R. D. Burman

घातक :- 
काशी नाथ बनारस के रहने वाले दयालु पहलवान और शंभू नाथ के कर्तव्यनिष्ठ दत्तक पुत्र हैं। शंभू नाथ, जो तंबर पत्र से सम्मानित स्वतंत्रता सेनानी थे, शहर में एक सम्मानित और प्रतिष्ठित व्यक्ति हैं। काशी, शंभू के साथ, शंभू के इलाज के लिए मुंबई आता है और अपने भाई शिव नाथ के साथ रहता है। काशी कॉलोनी में गौरी से मिलती है और उसे पसंद करने लगती है। उसे पता चलता है कि कॉलोनी को अत्याचारी गैंगस्टर, कात्या और उसके छह भाइयों द्वारा आतंकित किया जा रहा है। काशी के आगमन से पहले, सचदेव नामक एक निवासी ने कात्या के खिलाफ विद्रोह शुरू करने की कोशिश की, लेकिन उसने उसे बेरहमी से मार डाला, जिससे सचदेव की पत्नी मालती पागल हो गई। कात्या और उसके भाई काशी के दुश्मन बन जाते हैं जब वह मालती के साथ मारपीट करने की प्रक्रिया में उनके गुंडों की पिटाई करता है।

Ghatak :-
Kashi Nath is a kind-hearted wrestler and the dutiful adopted son of Shambhu Nath, living in Banaras. Shambhu Nath, who was a freedom fighter awarded with the Tambra Patra, is an honourable and respectable man in town. Kashi, along with Shambhu, comes to Mumbai for medical treatment for Shambhu and stays with his brother, Shiv Nath. Kashi meets Gauri in the colony and starts liking her. He learns that the colony is being terrorized by the tyrannical gangster, Katya, along with his six brothers. Before Kashi's arrival, a resident named Sachdev tried to initiate a revolt against Katya, but got ruthlessly killed by him, thereby making Malti, Sachdev's wife, go mad. Katya and his brothers become enemies with Kashi when he beats up their goons in the process of roughing up Malti.

Lyrics Of This Song:

Pan Hale To
Hale To Hiral Hansali
Are Re Eto Bole To Koyaladi
Pan Rade To
Ae Rade To Morala Ni Dheladi
Are Re Eto Patal Ni Putaladi
Are Re Eto Patal Ni Putaladi

He Harati Ne Farati
He Pavathe Pag Dhoti

Arise Mukhada Joti
Hiral Mari Evi Re Hetal Hati
He Eto Panch Hath Puri Kede Pataladi
Anmol Ujali Hati
Hiral Mara Haiya No Haralo Hati

snippet.description:
Hey Guys, I’m Jonathan Amaral, better known as Jonathan Gaming, a professional BGMI esports athlete and streamer.

Since the start of my journey, my dedication to the game has been defined by precision, consistency, and an unstoppable grind. As an assaulter, I’ve built a reputation for clutch performances and high-impact gameplay, earning respect in the BGMI community. 

Through years of dedication, I’ve honed my skills, adapting to every challenge and evolving with the game. Whether in high-stakes tournaments or streaming for the gaming community, my focus remains the same - pushing the limits and delivering top-tier gameplay.

snippet.title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x

Pre-order 'Play' out September 12: https://es.lnk.to/playID

The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4403: Trip Ki Taiyyari
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal gears up for his upcoming trip to the Himalayas, and the colony members also express interest. At the same time, he carefully explains to Bapuji how to handle the shop while he's away. Will Bapuji manage smoothly?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episode No - 4403
Produced By - Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. snippet.title: हादसे में कैसे बचा सीट 11A का यात्री?। Ahmedabad Plane Crash। Decode with Sudhir Chaudhary
snippet.description:
अहमदाबाद विमान हादसे में एक यात्री करिश्माई तरीके से बच गया. विमान में सीट नंबर 11A का यात्री विश्वास कुमार रमेश ठीक है. विश्वास ने जानकारी दी है कि सबकुछ उड़ान भरने के 30 सेकेंड में हो गया. जब आंख खुली तो चारों तरफ लाशें ही लाशें नज़र आ रही थीं. विश्वास का परिवार पिछले 20 सालों से लंदन में रह रहा है. वो भारत अपने परिजनों से मिलने के लिए आया था. 
     

#ahmedabad #planecrash #decodewithsudhirchaudhary #sudhirchaudhary
#ddnews #vijayrupani #ahmedabadairport #ahmedabadplanecrash

hi.title: छुट्टियों की झलकियाँ | परिवार के साथ ईद | केरल व्लॉग
hi.description:
छुट्टियों के दौरान बनाए गए व्लॉग मेरे लिए बहुत खास होते हैं क्योंकि वे यादें कई सालों बाद भी संजोकर रखी जाती हैं।
हम एक महीने के लिए केरल में हैं और उम्मीद है कि जितना संभव हो सके उतना व्लॉग बनाने की कोशिश करेंगे।

it.title: Scorci di vacanza | Eid con la famiglia | Vlog del Kerala
it.description:
I vlog delle vacanze sono molto speciali per me, perché sono ricordi che custodirò gelosamente anche molti anni dopo.
Saremo in Kerala per un mese e spero di riuscire a fare vlog il più possibile.

id.title: Sekilas tentang Liburan | Idul Fitri bersama Keluarga | Vlog Kerala
id.description:
Vlog liburan sangat istimewa bagi saya karena kenangan itu akan selalu dikenang bertahun-tahun kemudian.
Kami berada di Kerala selama sebulan dan mudah-mudahan akan mencoba membuat vlog sebanyak mungkin

fr-FR.title: Aperçus de vacances | Aïd en famille | Vlog du Kerala
fr-FR.description: Les vlogs de vacances sont très précieux pour moi, car ces souvenirs resteront gravés dans ma mémoire de nombreuses années. Nous sommes au Kerala pour un mois et nous espérons faire autant de vlogs que possible.

de-DE.title: Urlaubseinblicke | Eid mit der Familie | Kerala Vlog
de-DE.description:
Urlaubs-Vlogs sind für mich etwas ganz Besonderes, da diese Erinnerungen auch noch viele Jahre später in Ehren gehalten werden.
Wir sind einen Monat in Kerala und werden hoffentlich versuchen, so viel wie möglich zu vloggen.

es-US.title: Vistazos de vacaciones | Eid en familia | Vlog de Kerala
es-US.description:
Los vlogs de vacaciones son muy especiales para mí, ya que esos recuerdos se conservarán durante muchos años.
Estaremos en Kerala un mes y espero intentar vlogear todo lo que podamos.

pt-BR.title: Vislumbres de Férias | Eid com a Família | Vlog de Kerala
pt-BR.description:
Os vlogs de férias são muito especiais para mim, pois essas memórias serão guardadas com carinho por muitos e muitos anos.
Estamos em Kerala por um mês e esperamos tentar vlogar o máximo possível.

ja.title: 休暇のひととき | 家族と過ごすイード | ケーララ州Vlog
ja.description:
休暇中のVlogは私にとってとても特別なものです。何年も経っても、その思い出は大切に残るからです。
私たちは1ヶ月間ケーララに滞在しているので、できるだけ多くのVlogを投稿したいと思っています。

snippet.title: Finding Best Paschim Vihar Food With AI Purav Jha In Delhi | Tere Gully Mein Ep 107 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Be The First To Watch All Videos. Download the CurlyTales App: https://curlytale.page.link/DwNd

In this fun-filled episode of Tere Gully Mein, we meet India's Top Youtuber & the one who cracks us up with hilarious mimicry and crazy characters, it's none other than the OG Youtuber @Puravjha_  

This time we go out on the streets of Delhi's Paschim Vihar and explore some iconic hotspots there. Purav is a total foodie and this episode clearly proves that!  

From Little Chef's juicy rolls and wraps to his all-time comfort ice cream spot, Gianis and the ever-crowded Sandos restaurant which is popular among the locals for its north indian delicacies, this episode is your all-access food guide whenever you're in West Delhi. 

What else? Well, we also play a few fun games to bring out the real, candid side of Purav that included Never Have I Ever, a crazy Mimic challenge and ultimately the one where he gets to describe the fellow youtubers and content creators in one word each. It gets way too real! (Something you wouldn't want to miss!)

From talking about his first career break with Harsh Beniwal. his equation with him today to his lady love and his Bihari dialect, he talks about it very candidly. Purav also talks about his skincare routine (because of his girlfriend :D), his most expensive purchase till date and also shares his feelings on getting trolled.

Watch Purav Jha like never before! This video will make you fall in love with him again and will also make you admire his talent even more.

Tune in and drop your thoughts in the comments below!

snippet.title: குஜராத்தில் 242 பேருடன் விமானம் வெடித்தது ஏன் ahmedabad plane crash | A171 AI Flight | mayday alert
snippet.description:
#Partnership குஜராத் மாநிலம் ஆமதபாத்தில் 242 பேருடன் விமானம் விழுந்து நொறுங்கி இருப்பது மொத்த நாட்டையும் உலுக்கிப்போட்டுள்ளது.

ஆமதாபாத் ஏர்போர்ட்டில் இருந்து ஏர் இந்தியா ஏ171 என்ற விமானம் இன்று மதியம் 1:39 மணிக்கு 23வது நம்பர் ரன்வேயில் இருந்து லண்டனின் கேட்விக் gatwick ஏர்போர்ட்டுக்கு புறப்பட்டது.

விமானத்தில் 2 பைலட், 10 விமான ஊழியர்கள், 230 பயணிகள் என மொத்தம் 242 பேர் இருந்தனர்.

பயணிகளை பொறுத்தவரை 169 பேர் இந்தியாவை சேர்ந்தவர்கள். 53 பேர் பிரிட்டனை சேர்ந்தவர்கள். இது தவிர கனடாவை சேர்ந்த ஒருத்தர், போர்ச்சுக்கல்லை சேர்ந்த 7 பேரும் விமானத்தில் இருந்தனர்.

ரன்வேயில் இருந்து டேக் ஆப் ஆன அடுத்த சில நிமிடங்களில் விமானம் விபத்துக்குள்ளானது.

ஏர்போர்ட் பக்கத்தில் மேகானிநகர் meghaninagar என்ற இடத்தில் உள்ள மைதானத்தில் விமானம் விழுந்து நொறுங்கியது.

தரையில் மோதியதும் 242 பயணிகளுடன் விமானம் வெடித்து சிதறியது. இதில் மொத்த விமானமும் தீப்பிடித்து எரிந்தது.

விமானம் தாழ்வாக பறந்து தரையில் மோதி வெடிக்கும் வீடியோ வெளியாக நெஞ்சை பதற வைத்துள்ளது.

விமானம் தரையில் விழுந்து வெடித்ததும் விண்ணை முட்டும் அளவுக்கு புகை மூட்டம் கிளம்பியது. 7 தீயணைப்பு வண்டிகள் சம்பவ இடத்துக்கு விரைந்தன.

தீயணைப்பு வீரர்களுடன் போலீசார், பேரிடர் மீட்பு படையினரும் மீட்பு பணியில் ஈடுபட்டனர்.

விமானம் தரையில் மோதிய சில நிமிடங்களிலேயே கிட்டத்தட்ட முழுமையாக எரிந்து சாம்பலாகி விட்டது.


விமானம் விபத்தில் சிக்கியதற்கு என்ன காரணம் என்பது தெரியவில்லை. ஆனால், விமானம் வெடிப்பதற்கு முன்பு என்ன நடந்தது என்பது பற்றிய தகவல் இப்போது வெளியாகி உள்ளது.

அதாவது, மதியம் 1:39 மணிக்கு விமானம் டேக் ஆப் ஆக ஆரம்பித்த சில நிமடங்களிலேயே கோ-பைலட் மேடே Mayday அலர்ட் கொடுத்துள்ளார்.

மேடே அலர்ட் என்பது பயணிகளின் உயிருக்கு அச்சுறுத்தல் நேரும் போது பைலட்கள் கொடுக்கும் அலர்ட்.

மேடே மேடே என்று பயணிகளை பைலட்கள் எச்சரிப்பார்கள்.

அப்படி தான் விமானம் பறக்க ஆரம்பித்த சிறிது நேரத்தில் வான் கட்டுப்பாட்டு மையத்துக்கு கோ-பைலட் மேடே அலர்ட் கொடுத்திருக்கிறார்.

ஆனால் மறுகணமே கட்டுப்பாட்டு அறையுடனான தொடர்பை விமானம் இழந்து விட்டது.

அதாவது, மேடே அலர்ட் கொடுத்த மறுகணமே தரையில் விழுந்து விமானம் வெடித்திருக்க வேண்டும் என்று வான் கட்டுப்பாட்டு மையத்தில் இருந்து தகவல் வெளியாகி இருக்கிறது.

கடந்த ஆண்டு டிசம்பர் மாதம் தென்கொரியாவில் இப்படியொரு கோர விபத்து நடந்தது. விமானம் தரையிறங்கும் நேரத்தில் வெடித்து சிதறியது.

அப்போது விமானம் மீது ராட்சத பறவை ஒன்று மோதியது. அப்போதும் விமான பைலட்கள் மேடே அலர்ட் கொடுத்தனர்.

ஆனால் அடுத்த சில நிமிடங்களில் விமானம் வெடித்து சிதறி விட்டது. ஒருவர் கூட உயிர் பிழைக்கவில்லை.

ஆமதாபாத் விமான விபத்தும் மேடே அலர்ட் கொடுத்த சில நொடிகளில் நடந்திருக்கிறது. 242 பேரின் கதி என்னவென்று தெரியவில்லை.

விபத்துக்குள்ளான விமானத்தில் குஜராத்தின் முன்னாள் முதல்வர் விஜய் ரூபானியும் இருந்துள்ளார்.

விபத்து தொடர்பாக பிரதமர் மோடி, அமித்ஷா இரங்கல் தெரிவித்தனர். தேவையான நடவடிக்கைகளை எடுக்க குஜராத் முதல்வருக்கும், விமான போக்குவரத்து துறை அமைச்சருக்கும் உத்தரவிட்டனர்.#ahmedabadplanecrash #A171AIFlight #maydayalert #dinamalar

100 सेकंड में कैसे कम्पनी को हैक होने से बचाएगा अभिषेक बच्चन - Om Jai Jagdish -  ज़बरदस्त बेस्ट सीन - Anil Kapoor, Abhishek Bachchan - Om Jai Jagdish - 

Witness the heartwarming story of brotherhood and family values in "Om Jai Jagadish." Released in 2002, this Hindi film beautifully portrays the lives of three brothers and their unwavering bond despite facing various trials and tribulations. When their father passes away, the eldest brother, Om, selflessly takes on the responsibility of caring for his younger siblings, Jai and Jagadish. As they navigate life's challenges, including financial difficulties and personal aspirations, their unity is tested. Will their strong familial love withstand the pressures of the outside world? Experience a captivating narrative filled with emotion, drama, and memorable performances from a stellar cast.

◾ Film : Om Jai Jagadish.
◾ Director : Anupam Kher.
◾ Producer : Vashu Bhagnani.
◾ Cast : Anil Kapoor, Fardeen Khan, Abhishek Bachchan, Mahima Chaudhry, Urmila Matondkar, Pooja Batra.
